channel.description:
I did everything in the guide for the Automatic portforward thing and when I compile it says this javac: invalid flag: \AllGoFreePortForwarding.jar Usage: javac use -help for a list of possible options You have sucsessfully compiled Press any key to continue . . . I need help! I know thats not correct Code in the compiler.bat
@echo off color 0a title LahainaGeneration Compiler if exist "%programfiles%\Java" (call :compile "%programfiles%\Java\") else (goto error) :compile for /D %%x in ("%~1jdk*") do (set p="%%~x\bin\javac.exe") if defined p (%p% -cp .;. \AllGoFreePortForwarding.jar *java) if defined p (goto end) "C:/Program Files/Java\jdk1.6.0_20/bin/javac.exe" -cp .\AllGoFreePortForwarding.jar -d ./bin ./src/*.java :error echo You do not have Java installed. Please download it at the site that is about to load. "%programfiles%\Internet Explorer\iexplore.exe" http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp :end echo You have sucsessfully compiled pause exit
